sjc.parser

Class StaticJavaV4BaseVisitor<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • <any>
      • sjc.parser.StaticJavaV4BaseVisitor<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    StaticJavaV4Visitor<T>

    public class StaticJavaV4BaseVisitor<T>
extends <any>
implements StaticJavaV4Visitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of StaticJavaV4Visitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
